    Non-serializable, transient Binary data value abstraction.

    Serializable POJO abstraction for content item (e.g, Item), which should be either ContentNode or ContentProperty.

    Serializable POJO abstraction for content node (e.g, Node).

    Serializable POJO abstraction for a content property (e.g, Property).
